      <p class="entry-note">ATLAS is the shared instruction system that keeps Forgotten Industries portable: calm execution, archive-first defaults, Matthew-specific collaboration guidance, reusable templates, and named subroutines. Les Trois Témoins now have a local landing: Le Sauvegarder, Le Continuant, and Le Rédempteur.</p>
